    <body>
      <div type="transcription" xml:id="transcription_aad_0086" xml:lang="en">
        <div type="letter">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00299/" ed="1r" type="sheet"/>
          <div>
            <ab hand="#hand_gray_unident_0086_1"><!-- review -->
              <lb/>15/ B26/1
            </ab>
          </div>
          <div type="letter_message" hand="#hand_blue_auden">
            <opener>
              <dateline>
                <placeName>
                  <address xml:lang="de">
                    <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_2">Kirchste<unclear>tt</unclear>en (Westbahn)
                    <lb/>Hinterholz #6
                    <lb/>N.Ö</rs>
                  </address>
                </placeName>
                <date>
                  <lb/>Sept 17<hi rend="superscript"><unclear>th</unclear></hi>
                </date>
                <seg hand="#hand_gray_unident_0086_2"><!-- review -->
                  <date>
                    <lb/>September 1966
                  </date>
                </seg>
              </dateline>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Dear <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_78">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Spiel</rs>:
              </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
              <lb/>Thank you for your letter of Sept 15<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>.
              <lb/>I should be very pleased to read to th<unclear>e</unclear>
              <lb/><rs type="org" ref="#amp_organization_10">Osterreich<unclear>i</unclear>schen P.E.N<unclear>..</unclear></rs> The difficulty is
              <lb/>the date. I hav<unclear>e</unclear> to go to <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_17">Berlin</rs> next
              <lb/>Monday for rehearsals of <hi rend="underline" hand="#hand_blue_auden">Die Bass<unclear>a</unclear>riden</hi>
              <lb/>ret<unclear>uri</unclear>ng here on Sept 30<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. Then,because of
              <lb/>engagements in <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_239">England</rs>, I have to leave <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_10">Austria</rs>
              <lb/>earlier than I usually do, on Oct 7<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>This means, in fact , th<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="char"/><unclear>t</unclear> the only two
              <lb/>possible days for me are either Tuesday Oct 4<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
              <lb/>or Wednesday Oct 5<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>Could you let me know if either of th<unclear>ese</unclear>
              <lb/>da<unclear>te</unclear>s <unclear>i</unclear>s p<unclear>o</unclear>ssible for you, <unclear>&#8453;</unclear> Deutsche Sta<unclear>d</unclear>t<unclear>s</unclear>oper<unclear>.</unclear><!-- review -->
              <lb/>West Berlin.<!-- review -->
            </p>
            <closer>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Yours sincerely
              </salute>
              <signed>
                <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">W<unclear>.</unclear>H.Aude<unclear>&#7751;</unclear></rs>
              </signed>
            </closer>
          </div>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00300/" ed="1v" type="sheet"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
